    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J257">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Delight is as the flight --</l>
                    <l>Or in the Ratio of it,</l>
                    <l>As the Schools would say</l>
                    <l>The Rainbow's way --</l>
                    <l>A Skein</l>
                    <l>Flung colored, after Rain,</l>
                    <l>Would suit as bright,</l>
                    <l>Except that flight</l>
                    <l>Were Aliment --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>"If it would last"</l>
                    <l>I asked the East,</l>
                    <l>When that Bent Stripe</l>
                    <l>Struck up my childish</l>
                    <l>Firmament --</l>
                    <l>And I, for glee,</l>
                    <l>Took Rainbows, as the common way,</l>
                    <l>And empty Skies</l>
                    <l>The Eccentricity</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And so with Lives --</l>
                    <l>And so with Butterflies --</l>
                    <l>Seen magic -- through the fright</l>
                    <l>That they will cheat the sight --</l>
                    <l>And Dower latitudes far on --</l>
                    <l>Some sudden morn --</l>
                    <l>Our portion -- in the fashion --</l>
                    <l>Done --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
